message.content: cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.ET - The paper discusses the semantics of Prolog tracers and the Byrd's box model, which are related to programming languages and logic (cs.PL and cs.LO). It also discusses the implementation and limitations of tracers, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a declarative specification for tracers, which is related to formal methods and verification (cs.ET).
